        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "which is precisely (\") times the geometric mean of the terms on the left. Thus AM-GM shows that the terms under consideration on the left exceed those on the right; adding these inequalities over all k yields the desired result.",
